Vital Point to Capture?(39)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0\deflang1033\deflangfe1042{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par \b White to play\b0 .
\par Black's right side looks enough and it also seems he can make one eye on the left side.
\par
\par First of all, if Black plays he can live easily, so White has to attack.
\par Where is the vital point?
\par
\par
\par }
